msg: The pde-maven-plugin's author, Dan Tran, was able to advice me on what was missing from the pom config.  The shale clay plugin for eclipse now has a maven build.    The only dependency is having eclipse 3.2 installed with the PDE tools and configuring the eclipseInstall property for the pde-maven-plugin (SHALE-444).
This is an empty revision for padding.
